      "instruction": "<p>Rinse the <strong>brown rice</strong>, add it to a pot with plenty of <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 20-25 min or until tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain into a sieve and set aside, reserving the pot for later</p>",
