    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, add the <strong>diced chicken thigh</strong>,<strong> five-spice</strong> and a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> to a bowl and give everything a good mix up</p>",
